## Data Collection

This website only uses [posthog](https://posthog.com/) for simple anonymous
analytics and does not collect any personally identifiable information.

The data gathered by Posthog consists of:

  * Your IP address (displayed anonymized)
  * Date and time of visit
  * Pages visited
  * Browser and operating system info
  * Referring website

This data is employed to generate anonymous analytics concerning website
visits, sources of traffic, and similar data.
